Results.ReviewText: I tried this over the past few weeks, and I'm glad I did. Very smooth taste and perfect for morning, noon or night, to keep me going . Would definitely recommend.
Results.Title: lovely and smooth texture

Results.ReviewText: Perhaps my tastes are changing but I don't think so. This coffee is much weaker than in the past and I have to use much more to get the flavour that I am used to.
Results.Title: Not so strong

Results.ReviewText: I have drank this coffee for a number of years and always come back to it when i have tried other brands. Its rich taste makes me feel satisfied when drinking it.
Results.Title: My Favourite start to the day

Results.ReviewText: We bought this product last week, this is the best cup of instant coffee I have tasted in years.  Smooth as silk flowing down the throat with a great after taste.
Results.Title: Smooth as Gold

Results.ReviewText: I've used this coffee for years now, the taste is always consistent and visitors always complemented on my cups of coffee!  For the price there's nothing better.
Results.Title: I wouldn't buy anything else

Results.ReviewText: We drink this at work so it has to please a few people at once and overall it steals the show. A great coffee for us regular drinkers so I bought it for home too
Results.Title: Smooth enough to drink on a regular basis

Results.ReviewText: I've always thought Gold Blend worth the extra money because you get the extra quality - great rounded flavour as close to freshly brewed coffee as instant gets.
Results.Title: Gold Blend just got even better!

Results.ReviewText: Great flavor however leaves a residue like you find in a ground coffee, something that we are not keen on, one of the reasons that we drink an 'instant' coffee.
Results.Title: Great flavor however

Results.ReviewText:
This is the only coffee I buy!
I've tried other brands in the past but gold blend gives the richest & smoothest taste.. Always reliable & my go to coffee brand
Results.Title: Rich tasting coffee

Results.ReviewText: I can't resist the taste of Nescafe Gold Blend, it's usually my first thought as I wake up. My mornings would be unimaginable without Nescafe's great awakening.
Results.Title: That Indulging Taste

Results.ReviewText: Much preferred the taste of gold blend before it was changed.  It now has a powdery residue at the end of the cup which greatly ruins my once favourite coffee .
Results.Title: Prefer it before changed

Results.ReviewText:
This is a nice smooth coffee.  
The only trouble is it always leaves fine dregs of powder at the bottom of the cup which have settled to the bottom of the cup.
Results.Title: Nice Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I normally have a rival brand but bought nescafe as it was on offer. I will always but it from now on. Its taste is so smooth and it re-awakens your taste buds
Results.Title: Nescafe gold blend

Results.ReviewText: I need a good cup of coffee throughout the day to give me a little boost,i've tried numerous brands but nothing beats the delicious taste of Nescafe Gold Blend
Results.Title: Tried others but nothing beats Gold Blend

Results.ReviewText: I prefer the taste of Gold Blend to that of other coffee brands. It has a smooth taste that always brings me back for more.Great Flavour. No bitter aftertaste.
Results.Title: Smooth

Results.ReviewText: I alway buy this coffee its one of my go to brands I get very disapointed if its sold out in my local store.As this is my go to kick start brand every morning.
Results.Title: One of my fav's

Results.ReviewText: Normally have coffee of an espresso machine, having run out purchased what I thought might be an all round everyday coffee with taste and was not disappointed.
Results.Title: Good all rounder

Results.ReviewText: Well all I'll say is.....Its only the packaging that's changed, The contents inside are still the same  perfect blend as you'd expect. Why alter perfection!!!!
Results.Title: Only the packaging!!!

Results.ReviewText: A classic coffee blend that has stood the test of time, raises the bar from the run of the mill, enhances your coffee experience and represents excellent value
Results.Title: Golden Classic

ClientResponses.Response: Hey, during the recent recipe change, micro ground coffee was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee! It disappoints us to hear you're not a fan of the new recipe but thanks for letting us know!

Results.ReviewText: Why why why change the recipe to destroy a perfect coffee? The sludge left in the bottom the cup is awful.  If we wanted Barista Style we’d buy Barista Style.
Results.Title: Horrendous

Results.ReviewText:
Have been buying Nescafe for over 20 years.Like it's flavour and texture.
Also have a Nescafe Dolce Gusto machine.Luv the the different coffee pods for them.
Results.Title: Great coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have always enjoyed Nescafe Gold.  I particularly enjoy the smooth taste and distinctive flavour of this brand.  Nescafe is so reliable and always delivers.
Results.Title: Smooth Tasting

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee recently and WOW is it lovely, it's been a long time since we enjoyed an instant coffee this good, we will be getting this again I think.
Results.Title: Excellent Coffee

Results.ReviewText: the kick start to my day the full bodied coffee ,with great taste ,value for money ,this is the only coffee i drink ,as others brands do not even come close ,
Results.Title: the kick start to my day

Results.ReviewText:
I bought this coffee two weeeks ago, eye catching jar, easy to open / hold due to the shape of the jar.
Dissolved easily in water, nice taste not too bitter
Results.Title: Eye catching Jar

Results.ReviewText: The product has changed, same great taste but now leaves a black powdery sut at the bottom of the cup. I don't particularly like the sut but can live with it
Results.Title: Same great tatse

Results.ReviewText: This is a lovely smooth, not to strong coffee. It’s easy to drink time and time again. It’s definitely one that will be stocked up and staying in my cupboard
Results.Title: “Lovely”

Results.ReviewText: I have bought Gold Blend for as long as I can remember and it is the one coffee that tastes great anytime but is really great in the morning to get me going.
Results.Title: Morning Heaven

Results.ReviewText: I brought this instead of my usual brand and I'm so glad I did , it's a great coffee well blended nice taste and appearance. I will only by this from now on.
Results.Title: Lovley rich coffee taste

Results.ReviewText: Have been using gold blend for many years always first choice and never disappointed. Smooth flavour easy on the palette flavour.  Very good value for money
Results.Title: Great value instant coffe
